            | -p | ./profiles/basic-connection-org1.json |
            | -u | PeerAdmin |
            | -c | ./hlfv1/crypto-config/peerOrganizations/org1.example.com/users/Admin@org1.example.com/msp/signcerts/Admin@org1.example.com-cert.pem |
